00:46:35,393 --> 00:46:36,862
No, I don't like it!

690
00:46:36,862 --> 00:46:38,596
I don't like it, no.

691
00:46:38,596 --> 00:46:41,166
- I don't think it would work.
- Nobody wants to watch that.

692
00:46:41,166 --> 00:46:44,102
I'm not sure that they do.
Anyway, we've got a better idea,

693
00:46:44,102 --> 00:46:46,137
Okay, for our celebrities.

694
00:46:46,137 --> 00:46:49,207
