that's his plane.

750
00:49:50,388 --> 00:49:52,390
Hold on, everybody.
Here he comes.

751
00:49:52,390 --> 00:49:55,126
He is ready to jump.

752
00:49:55,126 --> 00:49:56,827
I'm ready!

753
00:49:56,827 --> 00:50:00,065
He is ready to jump.
